ZH: 我不想繼續下去了。
EN: I don't want to continue on.

ZH: 我們必須往前走，不能停下去。
EN: We must keep going, can't stop now.

ZH: 不管發生多麼困難，我會繼續下去。
EN: No matter how difficult things get, I will keep going.

ZH: 您必須走下去，不要輕易放棄。
EN: You must persevere, don't give up easily.

ZH: 我們已經走了很遠，接下去的路還有多長？
EN: We have come a long way, how much further is the road ahead?

ZH: 請繼續下去，別停下來。
EN: Please keep moving forward, don't stop.

ZH: 下雨了，我們還是繼續往前走吧。
EN: It's raining, let's keep going forward.

ZH: 我會跟在你後面，直到最後一刻。
EN: I will follow you until the very end.

ZH: 無論如何，我會一直走下去。
EN: No matter what, I will keep moving forward.

ZH: 請保持積極態度，繼續前進。
EN: Please maintain a positive attitude and move forward.

ZH: 只要有信心，任何困難都能克服。
EN: With confidence, any challenge can be overcome.

ZH: 讓我們一起攜手走到將來。
EN: Let's walk hand in hand into the future.

ZH: 無論遇到多少挑戰，我們都會一起度過。
EN: No matter how many challenges we face, we will overcome them together.

ZH: 我相信我們能夠一直堅持到底。
EN: I believe we can persist until the end.

ZH: 讓我們緊握彼此的手，向前走去。
EN: Let's hold each other's hands tightly and move forward.

ZH: 千里之行，始於足下。
EN: A journey of a thousand miles begins with a single step.

ZH: 這一路走來，我們都變得更堅強。
EN: Along this way, we have all become stronger.

ZH: 失敗不要緊，重要的是要繼續前進。
EN: Failure is not important, what matters is to keep moving forward.

ZH: 雖然道路艱辛，我們還是要繼續前進。
EN: Despite the difficult road, we must continue on.

ZH: 空機坪下去右拐。
EN: Take a right at the end of the empty runway.
